{"tid":1637814,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"傳牛奶公司下令配合警方 主動交7–11及萬寧CCTV","createTime":"2019-10-08T05:58:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T15:46:02.000Z","uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f5447ab1b19b9e7f354ce081ef27ee5b7b6f0c66","tid":1637814,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:58:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">唔好去萬寧買奶粉即退，因為人地拎唔返出黎賣。同埋唔好留單用左13日就退貨，因為萬寧要全數退返錢比客，好蝕架</span></span><br />\n<br />\n反送中修例風波遇上警方執法問題，令抗爭活動遍地開花。早前網上片段流傳7.28上環衝突當晚，信德中心一家7-11便利店店員拒讓警員內進。今日有傳牛奶公司已向內部發信，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要求7-11以後要配合警方予以放行，上月已主動把所有7-11及萬寧閉路電視向警方交出，以便追捕抗議人士。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n7-11及萬寧同屬於牛奶公司旗下商舖，牛奶公司旗下還有惠康、美心、星巴克等品牌，亦是大陸「永輝超市」的股東。《蘋果》正向牛奶公司查詢，暫未獲回覆。<br />\n<br />\n7月14日，沙田新城市廣場保安被指做「吳三桂」引領警員入商場，結果警方圍捕示威者爆發困獸鬥衝突，血浴商場，母公司新鴻基事後即使表明，沒有報警及對事件深表遺憾和難過，仍備受輿論批評，更被踢爆向警方交出閉路電視。之後多個商戶與屋苑均曾直接或間接拒絕警方進入私人地方執法。然而隨着北京介入向商界施壓，令商界在警方執法處理上陷入兩難，例如九倉旗下的海港城曾張貼聲明指「除非有罪案發生，警察請勿進入」」，之後遭官媒點名批鬥，告示現已消失。"},{"pid":"bda6b7be5380aa53e849e5be6e87c708fff5f244","tid":1637814,"uid":276916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:09:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"be9bccca938ba1c8d291536fac57edaef932be5c","tid":1637814,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:11:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wRW8tME.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwRW8tME.jpg&h=d8823b86&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sr9NKj0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsr9NKj0.jpg&h=3e7c71e5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6ffe93aeff360643c17fdb3119ee02ba694d9c1","tid":1637814,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:14:18.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">10月<span style=\"color: teal;\">8</span>日：<span style=\"color: orange;\">提款日</span></span></strong><br />\n各大銀行總行撳錢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1634001\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1634001</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">10月<span style=\"color: teal;\">9</span>日：<span style=\"color: orange;\">文宣日</span></span></strong><br />\n齊齊修補連儂牆<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">10月<span style=\"color: teal;\">10</span>日：<span style=\"color: orange;\">消費日</span></span></strong><br />\n全民幫襯黃色店鋪，18區排長龍<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1634353\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1634353</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JG49P0v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJG49P0v.jpg&h=bfdca82e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b5ead4655bb768a4198f03e3ac4be2b5900690d","tid":1637814,"uid":38761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:20:45.000Z","msg":"其實都唔洗傳啦，佢自己都唔出聲係Facebook否定，即係有羅！"},{"pid":"a08d190664985464339efb98b4905a56dd949e35","tid":1637814,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:24:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1778392c63b65a92f35d41168effeae37ae8322b","tid":1637814,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:35:15.000Z","msg":"老共叫佢比，佢敢唔比？"},{"pid":"b06e9448a2c0b2c86cf07b23f4c6e224336d132c","tid":1637814,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:35:51.000Z","msg":"歐美國家都不企出來<br />\n<br />\n支共當然要更進一步啦"},{"pid":"2af39c65e527258c760b9a35a4eddda6d8423002","tid":1637814,"uid":315796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:41:45.000Z","msg":"如果文件係屬實既話，歡迎加入裝修名單<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇下邊個施壓邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c332f30c1fd61a39a9e1814fd6ce3d071d57cec0","tid":1637814,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r